OL,3,CCouncil urges parents not to buy
OL,4,C'dangerous' smartphones for under 14s
OL,6,FSecondary school pupils talk to ITV
OL,7,FNews Meridian's Andy Dickenson about
OL,8,Fusing dumbphones instead of
OL,9,Fsmartphones.
OL,11,FBrighton and Hove Council has written
OL,12,Fto parents urging them not to buy
OL,13,Fsmartphones for their children until
OL,14,Fthey're 14.
OL,16,FCampaigners say early access to social
OL,17,Fmedia and other online content is
OL,18,Fharming children's development and
OL,19,Fwelfare. The council is now asking
OL,20,Fparents to sign a pact, agreeing to
OL,21,Fhold back.
