OL,3,CCouncil urges parents not to buy
OL,4,C'dangerous' smartphones for under 14s
OL,6,FIt comes as more schools clamp down on
OL,7,Fmobile phone use.
OL,9,FDorothy Stringer School is the third
OL,10,Fof 10 secondary schools in Brighton to
OL,11,Fintroduce a pouch-lock scheme that
OL,12,Fteachers say is already having
OL,13,Fprofound affects.
OL,15,FDeputy headteacher, Cassie Dale, said,
OL,16,F''We've only started it for the last
OL,17,Fthree weeks and students are already
OL,18,Fout and about chatting to each other.
