OL,6,F"There's more laughter, there's more
OL,7,Fface to face interaction, they
OL,8,Fgenuinely seem like a weight has been
OL,9,Flifted off their shoulders, much
OL,10,Fhappier around school."
OL,12,FBut as the smartphone-free childhood
OL,13,Fcampaign gathers pace, the council is
OL,14,Ftaking things a step further - writing
OL,15,Fto parents urging them to delay buying
OL,16,Ftheir children smartphones at all -
OL,17,Funtil they're 14.
