OL,7,Fgood for children, please don't do it,
OL,8,Fbut ultimately it is the parent's
OL,9,Fdecision."
OL,11,FSebastien Dehestin from Smartphone
OL,12,FFree Childhood said, ''It's been
OL,13,Flinked to increasing mental health
OL,14,Fissues, depression, lack of sleep,
OL,15,Fkids being unable to focus in class.
