OL,6,F"Here in Brighton and Hove, what we're
OL,7,Fhoping for is to make this a public
OL,8,Fhealth issue, which means reaching
OL,9,Fparents when they've just had a baby
OL,10,Fand encouraging them to keep eye
OL,11,Fcontact with their child because it's
OL,12,Fcrucially important for language and
OL,13,Fsocial functions.
OL,15,F''And also we are hoping to reach
OL,16,Fadults and make everyone reconsider
OL,17,Ftheir habits."
OL,19,FLessons not just for children but
